{"tid":2316634,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"瑪利諾神父宿舍地盤 發現20個戰時炸彈及1,000粒子彈要疏散","createTime":"2020-12-08T04:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T08:01:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0c15783508ae78c28c41e6218cbf9090d5587df6","tid":2316634,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:24:48.000Z","msg":"早上10時21分，港島赤柱村道44號瑪利諾神父宿舍地盤，警方接獲工人報警，指發現泥下埋了20個戰時炸彈、手榴彈和1,000粒子彈。爆炸品處理課封鎖現場處理，並疏散10多人。<br />\n<br />\n瑪利諾神父宿舍位於赤柱村道44號﹐古諮會在2009年3月建議列為一級歷史建築，惟當時受到業主反對，最終於2016年12月8日確定評級。它有逾80年歷史，資料顯示，一間海外註冊公司於2016年以7.6億元購入，並向城規會申請，擬於宿舍的西面斜坡興建兩座新大樓，同時挖空現時部份建築物，向外擴建一幢敞開式停車間連三層高的別墅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201208/X3NVOJSLXRCNJDGTT5XRWSZZ3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201208%2FX3NVOJSLXRCNJDGTT5XRWSZZ3E%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=b9aa4407\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201208%2FX3NVOJSLXRCNJDGTT5XRWSZZ3E%2F&h=b488558d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201208/X3NVOJSLXRCNJDGTT5XRWSZZ3E/</a>"},{"pid":"57b6379819dcfb1a551503c5ff5a0161a39e2962","tid":2316634,"uid":4574,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"犯咗國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c4aa1028babbe50a7e7a863445f8f359ae52f6","tid":2316634,"uid":335434,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"支聯辦：外部勢力長時期策劃向黑暴攬炒派提供武器鐵證如山不容抵賴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593fbc328b0853a1a57341b056d7fee235f5aa8c","tid":2316634,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7382154c6adaa4802e5601654d0e21ce20902a","tid":2316634,"uid"